CSS Classes
-----------
<label cssClasses={["my-class"]} />   // use for styling
<label cssName="my-name" />           // changes GTK node name (not a CSS class)


Key Events (GTK4)
-----------------
<window keymode={Astal.Keymode.ON_DEMAND}>
  <Gtk.EventControllerKey
    onKeyPressed={({ widget }, keyval) => {
      if (keyval === Gdk.KEY_Escape) widget.hide()
    }}
  />
</window>


